## ✅ How to Use on GitHub
1. Go to your repository → click **“Add file” → “Create new file” → name it `README.md`**  
2. Paste the above text.  
3. Commit the changes.  
4. Optionally, in the repository sidebar → under **About**, paste this short description:
   > “Python | CodeAlpha Cyber Security Internship Task 1 — Basic Network Sniffer using Scapy on Windows”

